Message.MsgText: UNRECOVERABLE_ERROR_CWSJS0007=CWSJS0007E: An internal error occurred. The string representation of an XID became corrupted.
Message.Explanation: This exception is unexpected. The cause is not immediately known.
Message.UserResponse: If the problem persists, additional information might be available if you search for the message ID on the following Web sites: WebSphere Application Server Support page: http://www.ibm.com/software/webservers/appserv/was/support/ WebSphere Application Server for z/OS Support page: http://www.ibm.com/software/webservers/appserv/zos_os390/support/ .

Message.MsgText: LOCALTX_FAIL_CWSJS0002=CWSJS0002E: An exception, {0}, was created during the processing of a transactional operation, causing the operation to fail.
Message.Explanation: The specified exception was created during the processing of a transactional operation. This exception caused the transactional operation to fail.
Message.UserResponse: Investigate the cause of the exception.

Message.MsgText: GLOBAL_ENLIST_NO_TX_CWSJS0005=CWSJS0005E: An attempt was made to perform work using an unenlisted XAResource.
Message.Explanation: An attempt was made to perform transacted work with an XAResource that is not enlisted in a global transaction.
Message.UserResponse: Do not attempt to perform transacted work in the scope of an unenlisted XAResource.

Message.MsgText: TX_SIZE_EXCEEDED_CWSJS0010=CWSJS0010E: The maximum number of operations that is permissable for a single transaction ({0}) is exceeded.
Message.Explanation: A limit of operations that can be performed in the scope of a single transaction exists. An attempt was made to perform more than this number of transacted operations using a single transaction.
Message.UserResponse: Reduce the number of operations that are attempted in the scope of any one transaction lower than the specified limit.

Message.Explanation: If the message does not give sufficient information, check previous messages for further help.
Message.UserResponse: See the accompanying error messages for further information.

Message.MsgText: DUPLICATE_COMPLETE_CWSJS0003=CWSJS0003E: An attempt was made to complete an already completed local transaction.
Message.Explanation: The commit, or rollback method of a local transaction was invoked after the transaction completed.
Message.UserResponse: Avoid making duplicate attempts to complete a transaction.

Message.MsgText: LOCAL_ENLIST_INTO_COMPLETED_CWSJS0004=CWSJS0004E: An attempt was made to perform work in the scope of a completed local transaction.
Message.Explanation: An attempt was made to perform a recoverable action using a local transaction that is already committed or rolled back.
Message.UserResponse: Do not attempt to perform new transacted work in the scope of a completed transaction.
